{"word":"G3756 - οὐ - ou - oo - + long","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οὐ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ou</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">oo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">+ long</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"மாட்டாது, வேண்டாம். ஒன்றுமில்லை - எதிர்மறை எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"nay, no"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Also <b>&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03BA;</b> <b>ouk</b> <i>ook</i> used before a vowel and <b>&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03C7;</b> <b>ouch</b> <i>ookh</i> before an aspirate. <p/>A primary word; the absolutely negative (compare <a href=\"#/G3361 - μή - mḗ - may/3361\">G3361</a>) adverb; <i>no</i> or <i>not</i>: - + long, nay, neither, never, no (X man), none, [can-] not, + nothing, + special, un ([-worthy]), when, + without, + yet but. See also <a href=\"#/G3364 - οὐ μή - ou mḗ - oo may/3364\">G3364</a>, <a href=\"#/G3372 - μῆκος - mēkos - may'-kos/3372\">G3372</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}